This paper proposes a novel technology for classifier ensemble, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper focuses on optimizing the diversity measure in classifier ensembles, which is a key problem in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
